<number box="[1234,1246,1086,1110]" pageId="6" pageNumber="597" value="3.0">3</number>
at level 0.45 of idiosoma length. Gp- 
<number box="[389,403,1122,1146]" pageId="6" pageNumber="597" value="4.0">4</number>
at level 0.72 of idiosoma. PD length 
<number box="[822,866,1122,1146]" pageId="6" pageNumber="597" value="138.0">138</number>
