, width 
<number box="[268,341,1302,1326]" pageId="6" pageNumber="597" value="35.41">35, 41</number>
μm from anterior edge of GA. A single pair of pgs close 
<collectingCountry box="[1016,1088,1302,1326]" name="Togo" pageId="6" pageNumber="597">to GO</collectingCountry>
